Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.04,0:01:01.66,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur2}光が待っている
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.66,0:01:05.12,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur2}I've got you You've got me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.12,0:01:08.42,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}最後まで進んで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.75,0:01:12.42,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur2}Oh in the night we can wish on a star
