Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.35,0:01:21.02,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}手を伸ばし続けた{\fscx50} {\fscx100}big dream
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.02,0:01:24.69,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}誰かの目には{\fscx50} {\fscx100}it's a daydream
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.69,0:01:28.86,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}“All the stars that shine brightest, Burn out the fastest”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.86,0:01:32.19,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur2}ぼくら越えていける
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.19,0:01:35.45,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}誰も知らない{\fscx50} {\fscx100}tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.45,0:01:39.33,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur2}心の声だけ{\fscx50} {\fscx100}follow
